{"tid":2247770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"姐姐」穆斯林　TVB劇常回教徒　戲中妙用回教徒　南洋一堆回教徒","createTime":"2020-10-18T06:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T06:14:58.000Z","uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5171468b938a8baa80253ccaf7fc76119e2e646b","tid":2247770,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20201018061041/https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1317370350653435905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20201018061041%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1317370350653435905&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=5224c1f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20201018061041/https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1317370350653435905</a><br />\n<br />\n很多香港人養大他自己的「姐姐」本身就是穆斯林；以前TVB電視劇時常都會有穆斯林出現，只不過以前不是叫穆斯林而是叫回教徒；戲劇裡一男對多女不知劇情怎收尾好，結局就會去南洋信回教就可以聚四個老婆happy ending；南洋一堆回教徒。"}]}